Package deco2800.thomas.entities

Class AbstractEntity

java.lang.Object
deco2800.thomas.entities.AbstractEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Renderable, java.lang.Comparable<AbstractEntity>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AgentEntity, GrassTuft, StaticEntity
public abstract class AbstractEntity
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<AbstractEntity>, Renderable
AbstractEntity is an item that can exist in both 3D and 2D worlds. AbstractEntities are rendered by Render2D and Render3D. An item that does not need to be rendered should not be a WorldEntity.
